| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1118 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 318b3c1a-bbe1-5c69-8869-b28691b6088e"
